data.description: Welcome to this cute and cozy 3-bedroom ranch in desirable Mentor, Ohio.  This home is on a quiet and remote street just off Lakeshore.  5555 Francis has it all in terms of location, the schools are just minutes away.  Community Parks and Pools and other amenities such as golf courses and Headlines Beach are just a short drive away.  The deck and the backyard are the perfect spot to settle in and unwind with family and friends.  The seller has paid to have a new roof installed (updated 1/25)! Schedule your showing today!
